Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好的看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为终有一天你也会继承这份使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光? 『调律』是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将妖怪送往那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 爷爷 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:44.69,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(320,340)}你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也并不是什么稀奇的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔带来见下面也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是 也不仅仅是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 因为大家都评价说很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想亲眼所见一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…你遇到的就只有那自称乱射魔的小兄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是谨慎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不露尾巴  那只狐狸混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只喜爱恶作剧的狐狸在城镇周围徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你不用太过于在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东铃 居住在樱真镇这段期间 要暂时约束你的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全信任曾让城镇陷于危险之中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是我 还是这座城镇都不会如此宽容的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是去上学的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是找寻能寄住的打工地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边工作 自己挣取学费
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我引起了那么大的骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是知道后才来这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是为妖怪而建的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我还有公事在身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细的事情就问秋名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 我把秋名先生带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有段时间没见了吧 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然也来这里露个脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有很多的事情要忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是妖怪生活商讨所所长 比泉秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇上生活的全面安排都是由他那管理的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么问题的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么人类会做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是妖怪的城镇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被讨厌了呢 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和人类的关系会如此亲近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇有它的规则所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护妖怪的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这个城镇住下的话 就得听秋名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被『七乡』所包围的范围之内大致都张开了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看了地图就会了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上只需要记住\N过桥后就是安全的 那就没什么问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是车站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分的商店都聚集在那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道有很多的妖怪在 你也不用太在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是专门为妖怪而设立的 所以不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这个也是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 车站前有银行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了吗 在车站前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗 由我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想早点赏花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱色遍染的城镇 一定相当美丽的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区长 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是『七乡』吗 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个必要 已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去元老院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得把城镇的吉祥物用狸怎么样 狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会给人种被哄骗了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比猪要好点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说起来\N你听说炸猪排店有会笑的猪的图画没？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是打算去吃蒙古烤肉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但结界外面有只狐狸 去吃不成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍 城镇的吉祥物用哺乳类可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊猫之类的不也很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个可是猛兽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在着冷气的房间里像糟老头似的懒来懒去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来完全就像个懒虫的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很凶暴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给它取名叫 牛舌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是食材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是挺悠哉 但貌似能看到某现实的未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这概念才是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的很晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 桃华一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀 言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 被元老院给传召了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫铃的孩子来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次的那个『不死人』吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是有个公园的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那个人类在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 对公务的怠慢也太随意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位…不是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 你是说恭助？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把角亮出来给你看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  去事务所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话给秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妖怪的城镇 让人类当所长真是够奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此 我从前也是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那人的危机意识也太过薄弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谈论的问题的要点不是这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 现在眼前就有一个正在困惑中的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也很清楚 他是城镇必不可少的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必不可少？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够『调律』的只有比泉家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将妖怪的灵魂送入另一个的世界\N也就是妖怪的世界能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了解救在这个世界暴走的妖怪\N也只有这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用秋名的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是被称为解救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在了 在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃华 没有必要帮这种男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别称呼我为「这种男人」啊  妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别躲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是杀了妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为是妖怪 所以杀了它也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为对方不是人类 就可以这样开怀大笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名不是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  是我解释的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前爷爷也是这么说我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也可以看成是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是不顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是把她送回事务所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没有印章的话 签个名就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迁入申请只是个形式罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这公寓附近有人类居住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有两户人家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他地方可选了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我们也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是人类 也不都是坏人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是这镇上住着的人都已经习惯和妖怪为邻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 老在意这些的话 连学校都去不了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点伤应该完全没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们妖怪不都很强的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说人类的语言 说几句妖怪语来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要…不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类无论怎么伤害妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着妖怪难受也都若无其事一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不会有这样的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我看起来也是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本也是人类 看起来像那类人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定有着「人类的时候真好」这样的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『花』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为现在也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉吗…很难回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 根据居民所述 是突然爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是由于妖怪的力量暴走所致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的事可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有前例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 再来做点愉快的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 从未听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当事人原本就是一个拥有很强妖力的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其力量在瞬间爆发出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的 怎么可能暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当事人口述说 在力量爆发之前 身体发热 无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口述说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被某种东西附身上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么认为的 但却找不到任何痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  又发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我自己也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己未能察觉的情况下 妖力就暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请详细告诉我经过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才已经跟警察说明过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你再说明一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 秋名在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他打过电话 没人接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象也没在事务所里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我绝对不要干消灭妖怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你所有背负的使命 终有一天你会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承受着那样的罪过\N正是因为你有着要保护的事物存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为比泉家之人 这是非做不可之事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在动摇什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校我也不会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是和姬约定好了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我不知道会同人类一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人类一起生活的话 很快就会习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认为没事 而我却很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护城镇  就必须进行『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被说了几句 就变得如此心神不定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的决心就只有这点程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有决心 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人称为杀人者 我也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护城镇 你的使命…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名你所做的并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小在这城镇中长大 身为妖怪的我是如此坚信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样都还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的…我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事务所 在事务所发生了暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是铃 东铃的妖力正在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍 布下结界 不要让人接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言叶 恭助 先防止暴走造成更大的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『笼』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『笼』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『笼』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要怎么样才能阻止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 我抑制的这段时间 你们快去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用『调律』的话 便能减轻妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃呢 要把她送走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实的呆在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算杀掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要杀掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 比泉家的人杀害过妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若无其事 毫无痛苦 一直都在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在内心却一直都明白「不能做这样的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样 如果这力量能保护他人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有坚信这力量是必须的妖怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不是铃的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家伙在操纵着妖怪的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『调律』…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺努力的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越期待了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌妖怪的人类是不会做这样的事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…帖符的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 你要喜欢那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说啦 别用哺乳类的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用这当食物的名字你也这么认为？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛舌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:21:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:21:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢一直以来的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.06,0:22:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝宝兰店送餐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉烧面两份 馄饨面一份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两千四百日圆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名表现的像主角一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.69,0:23:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说些什么啊
